  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WARNING: this game has thousands of bugs (but they're features). <strong>Shoot them</strong>, or they'll eat your pumpkins! </h2><br><br>No micro-transactions, DLC, or in-game purchases. You get the full game for free!<br><br>You're free to listen to your favorite music while playing, as this game has no music of its own.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <br><br>Get competitive on the <strong>leaderboards</strong>! Your score is <strong>the amount of bugs you killed.</strong> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/eb32e2bd3077c9fda10c4e8e59f6c6c2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=180 height=70 /></span><br><br>Are you a shotgun person, a sniper rifle person, or an assault rifle person? Try them out to find your favourite. <br>Each has a unique play style with strengths and drawbacks! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/a0f4c3e01d7fb82377f003a1514f3733.webp?t=1667069322\" width=144 height=50 /></span><br><br>When you level up, you are given a choice of three random gun mods. <br><br>Earn coins when you play, and spend them on upgrades! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/b7ce04d9147701de6f3852c24298c29a.avif?t=1667069322\" width=290 height=227 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Time Clock</h2> <br>Want to sit back, relax, and shoot some bugs? Play the game on <strong>normal speed</strong>. <br><br>Looking for an intense challenge? Try the game on <strong>2x speed</strong>, or even unlock <strong>4x speed!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><br>W, A, S and D to move. <br><br>Use the mouse to aim, and left click to shoot.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/e4b88c1ceecfeb745cedab807ded37da.avif?t=1667069322\" width=402 height=89 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/5df8693856e2c377220b687d4d5e86e4.avif?t=1667069322\" width=410 height=134 /></span><br><br>Feel free to leave a review.<br><br>Enjoy!<br><br>Harvest 10 pumpkins to earn this trophy:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/4a8b092675ee27c3b7a0529cfdc0c430.avif?t=1667069322\" width=160 height=300 /></span><br><br>What is the highest rank you can achieve? Harvest more pumpkins to improve your rank!<br>Grow a huuuuuge pumpkin patch!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WARNING: this game has thousands of bugs (but they're features). <strong>Shoot them</strong>, or they'll eat your pumpkins! </h2><br><br>No micro-transactions, DLC, or in-game purchases. You get the full game for free!<br><br>You're free to listen to your favorite music while playing, as this game has no music of its own.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/1b336003b29a73a6bc03ee7dcfa21ae2.avif?t=1667069322\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <br><br>Get competitive on the <strong>leaderboards</strong>! Your score is <strong>the amount of bugs you killed.</strong> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/951220/extras/eb32e2bd3077c9fda10c4e8e59f6c6c2.avif?t=1667069322